title: The White Raven
description: Hippie/fairy/mountain theme coffee and tea house. Offers bagels with vegetarian and vegan spreads available. Pastries include vegan cookies and brownies. Dairy free milk options for drinks. Roomy, cozy reading area and a front table seating area. Has Wi-Fi and computer rental. There is a gift shop with greeting cards, kids books, art kiche, glass pipes, incense, candles, and stash boxes.
